UPhaahla uthe bazokubhekisisa lokhu ukuze bangenele ngoba akukwazi ukuthi kungathi kuliwa nesinye isimo sezempilo bese abantu beba kwenye ingozi. Ukusho lokhu ekhuluma ngeSonto emuva kokudedelwa kocwaningo olwenziwe yiHuman Sciences Research Council ngomthelela weCorona nolwazi abantu abanalo ngayo. Umbiko uveza ukuthi * -13.2% wabantu abakwazi ukuthola imishanguzo ngenxa yesimo. “Kubalulekile ukuthi abantu baqhubeke bakwazi ukuthola imishanguzo yabo yezempilo. Sizoyibhekisisa eyombiko wocwaningo ngoba iqukethe izinto ezibalulekile.” Umbiko ubuye waveza ukuthi abantu abangaphezu kuka-20% abanamali yokuthenga ukudla. Ucwaningo lwenziwe kubantu abawu-19 330. “U-24% wabantu uzwakalise ukungabi namali yokuthenga ukudla. Cishe abangaphezu kukahhafu abahlala emijondolo abangenamali.” Abaphakathi kuka-45% kuya ku-63% bathe kuzoba nzima ukukhokhela izikweletu zabo nokuthola imali ukuze bakwazi ukondla imindeni yabo.